cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MA, cs.SY, cs.RO 

This paper is about modelling and exploiting teammates' policies in cooperative multi-agent systems using reinforcement learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.RO (Robotics).
